Class FileNames

  • java.lang.Object
    • FileNames

  • public class FileNames
extends java.lang.Object
    The FileNames class is a resource of functions to handle different file formats. It allows manipulations of the file format in terms of extension-editing and file-renaming.
    Author:
    Gina
